Environment - windows
    1. download Brackets at http://brackets.io/
    2. install three extentions:
        2-1. Emmet - installed by searching
        2-2. Custom Work - installed by searching
        2-3. Beautify - install by URL: https://github.com/brackets-beautify/brackets-beautify/archive/master.zip
    3. use customize settings 
        3-1. download the settings at https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/31101157/snippets-brackets.json to a folder
        3-2. open Emmet > Preference...
        3-3. type the absolute folder path in 3-1

Environment - ubuntu 14.04
    1. install brackets by ppa
        $sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/brackets
        $sudo apt-get update
        $sudo apt-get install brackets
    2. install three extentions:
        2-1. Emmet - installed by searching
        2-2. Custom Work - installed by searching
        2-3. Beautify - install by URL: https://github.com/brackets-beautify/brackets-beautify/archive/master.zip
    3. use customize settings 
        3-1. download the settings at https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/31101157/snippets-brackets.json to a folder
        3-2. open Emmet > Preference...
        3-3. type the absolute folder path in 3-1, such as home/Username/FolderName/
        
test 
    1. open a existing folder
    2. create a new file and save it with .html extension name
    3. type "html:bs" then press tab
    4. success if the following code is shown:
        <html>
        <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8">
            <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1.0">
            <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
            <meta name="renderer" content="webkit">
            <title>title</title>
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        </head>
        <body>
            <div class="container">bootstrap</div>
            <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
            <script src="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        </body>
        </html>